  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Which expression is equivalent to&nbsp;<math alttext=\"13 x squared minus 7 x squared\"><mrow><mn>13</mn></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mrow><mn>7</mn></mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>?</p>",
