ext=\"13 x squared minus 7 x squared\"><mn>13</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice C is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"13 x squared plus 7 x squared\"><mn>13</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"13 x squared minus 7 x squared\"><mn>13</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice D is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
